text: Quaint and comfortable!  Me and my family really liked being close to the city and around the corner from the most amazing Juice place... Oh and walks to the River.  Good times. Our host was amazing, gave us advice, checked in on us and even ET us use her Pack-N-Play for our infant so we didn't have to lug it from California.  I recommend this little bungalow highly.
title: Eastside Bungalow SXSW/dwntwn
